{"tid":1401282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊行 破壞 防守 係三個完全唔同的概念","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T14:44:09.000Z","uid":47659,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"25b298d99f372c71a10601cf441b3af3bc8b8b1b","tid":1401282,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:33:20.000Z","msg":"今日好多手足返mk死守<br />\n最後都係有手捉被拉.<br />\n<br />\n做每樣野之前 真係要諗清楚<br />\n<br />\n遊行係和理非手段 唔多解釋<br />\n<br />\n破壞 係震攝, 表達訴求同有時係防守既手段<br />\n<br />\n而防守係增加狗既清場成本去嘗試令佢地心身俱疲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">除此之後 除非你可以防守到有政治意義既機關 如立法會<br />\n又或者想長時間癱瘓交通 例如今日有人提出守紅隧<br />\n否則 我暫時諗唔到防守既用途</span><br />\n<br />\n無成效而有成本既野又點解咁堅持一定要做?<br />\n<br />\n歡迎賜教指正"},{"pid":"bb40cf2f7f92505521980121baff41bd6327dea1","tid":1401282,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:35:51.000Z","msg":"今日死守mk呢個防守係完全戰略失敗<br />\n唔好話我五毛, 擺明係明知有伏都照有人放風叫前線返旺角<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要防守就要問清楚自己為左咩野而防守<br />\n投放既資源同風險又值唔值得</span>"},{"pid":"446f38f44908b035f7bd1cca0ce1007ea1d23736","tid":1401282,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:38:30.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"80cc5c7b411a4ebbfa0c5fd562a7db4b2e18c502","tid":1401282,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b99e4aeba3fc1f1cd005d70872fa42e74e07ec","tid":1401282,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:39:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b31ec2214c932faf36ecfd425925be34d19e2465","tid":1401282,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:42:10.000Z","msg":"三樣野入面最唔BUY既唔係破壞<br />\n而係防守<br />\n<br />\n破壞雖然一定有罪但因為時間短被捕風險相對低<br />\n防守呢? 防守時被清場, 你就算企行人路佢都會拉你<br />\n<br />\n所以?"},{"pid":"be5024aec5058380aea52b07b17d9ace904248be","tid":1401282,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:44:09.000Z","msg":"?"}]}